梦剧场推出新专辑《Parasomnia》，收录技术新歌《Night Terror》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/dream-theater-announce-new-album-parasomnia-with-technical-new-track-night-terror-3801722?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dream-theater-宣布新专辑异态睡眠与技术新曲目夜惊Surej SinghFri, 11 Oct 2024 05:44:33 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3801722 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>标志着回归鼓手 Mike Portnoy 自 2009 年以来与乐队合作的第一首作品</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dream-theater-announce-new-album-parasomnia-with-technical-new-track-night-terror-3801722">梦剧院宣布新专辑“Parasomnia”后，其技术新曲目“Night Terror”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dream-theater">梦剧场</a>宣布了他们的新专辑《Parasomnia》，并分享了令人惊叹的新单曲《Night Terror》——请在下面了解所有详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/heriot-30-09-2024-3798080">NME 封面：赫瑞特已准备好掀起地狱</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（10 月 10 日），这支前卫金属乐队<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DA9GKhfImH-/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在社交媒体上</a>宣布了《Parasomnia》，这将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drummer-mike-portnoy-has-rejoined-dream-theater-3521331">他们自 2009 年的《Dark Clouds &amp; Silver Linings》以来与创始成员兼鼓手 Mike Portnoy 合作的首张唱片</a>。</p><p> 《Parasomnia》将成为乐队的第 16 张录音室专辑，也是与 Portnoy 合作的第 11 张录音室专辑。该专辑预计于 2025 年 2 月 7 日发行。《Parasomnia》将于今天晚些时候（10 月 11 日）开始接受预订。</p><p>为了庆祝专辑的发布，乐队还分享了一首新单曲“Night Terror”及其随附的音乐视频。这首近 10 分钟长的歌曲体现了迈克·波特诺伊 (Mike Portnoy) 的技术鼓风格以及乐队其他成员的标志性的古怪风格。</p><p>请听下面的“夜惊”。 </p><p><iframe title="梦剧场 - 夜惊（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2IPT60hvGw4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他们通过新闻稿描述了这张专辑：“这张专辑标志着我们作为乐队成员和兄弟的特殊新篇章的开始。这张专辑不仅代表了我们作为音乐家的成长，也代表了我们过去四十年共同踏上的旅程。”</p><p>梦剧院将于今年秋天与波特诺伊一起进行首次巡演，以庆祝其成立 40 周年，并于 10 月 20 日在伦敦演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dream-theater-announce-40th-anniversary-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3615300">，拉开欧洲巡演的序幕</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fdream-theater-tickets%2Fartist%2F744581" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3801724" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801724" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801724" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dream-theater-parasomnia-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801724" class="wp-caption-text">梦剧场《异态睡眠》封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>梦剧院的《Parasomnia》曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.《在墨菲斯的怀抱》</strong><br /> <strong>2.《夜惊》</strong><br /> <strong>3.《破碎的人》</strong><br /> <strong>4.《睡着了》</strong><br /> <strong>5.《午夜弥赛亚》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“我们在做梦吗？”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“扭转时钟”</strong><br /> <strong>8.《影子人事件》</strong></p><p>四月，波特诺伊告诉歌迷， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mike-portnoy-says-dream-theater-are-blown-away-by-new-album-3611663">乐队对他们迄今为止所拥有的材料感到“震惊”</a> ，并调侃道：“我们迫不及待地想让你们所有人听到这个……但是耐心点，一切都会在适当的时候揭晓……” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5JnRItP622/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div st