m/artists/cage-the-elephant">The Elephant</a>将加入阵容。</p><p>上个月有报道称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-reportedly-seeking-established-acts-to-support-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793095">利亚姆·加拉格尔正在寻求“既定行为”出现在该法案中</a>。主唱此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-jokes-about-joint-blur-tour-fuels-speculation-of-manic-street-preachers-or-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-3799791">建议 Manic Street Preachers 和 Richard Ashcroft 可以担任开场嘉宾</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/blossoms-interview-tom-ogden-gary-album-3796418">Blossoms 最近与<em>NME</em>讨论了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-on-supporting-oasis-if-we-get-asked-the-bags-are-packed-and-wed-smash-it-3799233">在 Live &#39;25 演出中支持 Oasis 的可能性</a>。在 Liam 在网上对这两个乐队进行猛烈抨击后，目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-doesnt-look-like-suede-will-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-3795466">看来 Suede</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-on-why-they-couldnt-really-give-a-shit-about-the-oasis-reunion-3793122">Fontaines DC 不太可能出现在阵容中</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" id="291703648" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?start=1629&amp;enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" width="100%" height="392" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-gtm-yt-inspected-6="true" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-and-noel-wont-be-doing-oasis-interviews-3801412">利亚姆表示，他和诺埃尔不打算就他们期待已久的重聚进行任何采访</a>。 “我们害怕媒体问我们侵入性的问题，并试图找出我们关系中的漏洞，”他解释道。</p><p>主持人还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/is-liam-gallagher-teasing-us-with-a-new-oasis-album-its-already-finished-3791619">告诉粉丝们，一张新的Oasis专辑是“已经完成的”</a> ，并向另一个粉丝重申了这一说法：“这是在袋子伴侣中他妈的空气。”</p><p>据报道，上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-reportedly-seeking-established-acts-to-support-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793095">LG正在寻找为英国和爱尔兰乐队开放的“既定行为”</a> 。此后，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-jokes-about-joint-blur-tour-fuels-speculation-of-manic-street-preachers-or-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-3799791">建议狂躁的街道传教士和理查德·阿什克罗夫特（Richard Ashcroft）可以接受支持插槽</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/blossoms-interview-tom-ogden-gary-album-3796418">Blossoms最近与<em>NME</em>谈到了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-on-supporting-oasis-if-we-get-asked-the-bags-are-packed-and-wed-smash-it-3799233">在<em>Live &#39;25</em> Dates中出现在该法案中的可能性</a>。在 Liam 在网上对这两个乐队进行猛烈抨击后，目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-doesnt-look-like-suede-will-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-3795466">看来 Suede</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-on-why-they-couldnt-really-give-a-shit-about-the-oasis-reunion-3793122">Fontaines DC 不太可能出现在阵容中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">绿洲后为澳大利亚2025年聚会之旅增加了更多日期，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
